<body>
<h1> Syntax </h1>
<br>
ask [mob] [topic] : askes the mob about the topic<br>
OR<br>
ask [mob] about [topic]<br>
<br>
<h1> Description </h1>
<br>
Ask is used if you want to ask a mob about a subject.  For example, in<br>
Chiiron you would ask the bartender about the boulder to the east of<br>
town, by typing 'ask barkeep boulder'.  <br>
